room_title: Escape room "Medieval Heist" by Rush Hour Escapes in Raleigh - Durham
review: So much fun!!! Highly recommend it. We did the Medieval Heist. Can’t wait to try the other room when we come back to North Carolina.

room_title: Escape room "Medieval Heist" by Rush Hour Escapes in Raleigh - Durham
review: Had a great time in the Medieval Heist Room with my women’s church group! We escaped with 7 minutes to spare! Love how everyone works together to figure it out! Would be a great team building activity.

room_title: Escape room "Medieval Heist" by Rush Hour Escapes in Raleigh - Durham
review: We escaped from the Medieval Heist room on our double date and I had a blast! I cant wait to bring the kids.
